The quality of beer label affixed his signature experienced brewer Czech Jiri Tomasek, once participated in the establishment of Utenos brewery.
Pagamintas "Lidl Lietuva" užsakymu. Light & expressive. Išraiškingo apynių ir salyklo aromato, aukso spalvos alus išsiskiriantis tankia, balta puta.

Utenos delivers beer cocktails beer Radler Lemon. Light beer, juice ctirinų, pleasant hop aroma - it features for Radl has become so popular and well liked throughout Europe.

According to legend, Radl (German Radeln - "cycling") born in the scorching heat in the summer of 1922, a pub, one of Bavaria. Its owner cyclists traveling through the country decided to beer to flavor carbonated drink with fruit juice.

This summery taste of light beer and orange juice cocktail, exuding an unexpected sweetness, acidity and subtle hop bitterness combination.

Oranges - the most common citrus fruit in the world, the absence of growth in our country, but the Lithuanians familiar fruits. So the taste and very popular beer cocktails and juices and soft drinks categories.

Utenos Radler, only 2% of alcohol. volume strength, easily aerated, making it particularly suitable for the summer. This beer cocktail naturalness sign - a cloudy liquid, and fruit resulting precipitate. So, before enjoying it is recommended that the bottle several times to turn easily in your hand, the fruit particles disperse.

International market research company Nielsen analyzed the 2012 sales figures, Utenos Radler "even gave two awards:" Best New 2012. Lithuania Product "and" Best Product category of mild alcohol Lithuania.
